      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         $SB210    BEGSR
      *
      *テーブルクリア
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TKT1
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TKT2
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TKT3
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TKTN
     C                     MOVE *ALL'0'   TSRY
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TKAI
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TISK
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TZKB
     C                     MOVE *ALL' '   TLTB
     C                     MOVE *ALL'0'   TDTN
